.B "int" hw_ep_set_halt
.BI "(struct ci_hdrc *ci "  ","
.BI "int num "  ","
.BI "int dir "  ","
.BI "int value "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ci" 12
the controller
.IP "num" 12
endpoint number
.IP "dir" 12
endpoint direction
.IP "value" 12
true => stall, false => unstall
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function returns an error code
